Name: Cable Clutter
About the game: Cable Clutter is a puzzle game where objects can be connected to each other to change their behaviour. Puzzles can be solved by pressing buttons, automation, and some head scratching. The game contains 48 levels that teach the player the mechanics and leads them to the solution of more and more complex problems.
